# Implement Quick Toast Notification

## Goal Description
Implement a "Quick Notification" (Toast) system that appears when a user adds an item to the cart, replacing the default behavior (which was previously auto-opening the cart).

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will creating a new `ToastContext` and `Toast` component to handle global notifications.

## Proposed Changes

### Frontend (Client)
#### [NEW] [ToastContext.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/App/src/contexts/ToastContext.tsx)
- Create a context to manage toast state (message, type, visible).
- Provide a `showToast(message, type)` function.

